’Щ@963e757988d9eb5104aa71e46454d5b8b82b11117af9e2249aa3cc3f4bf17e74ЪћTitle: title: polars selector by-dtype
Path: Examples
Content:
Create a selector for numeric columns
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> polars selector by-dtype i64 f64


```
Double all integer columns using with-column
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> [[a b c]; [1 2 "x"] [3 4 "y"]]
                    | polars into-df
                    | polars with-column ((polars selector by-dtype i64) * 2)
                    | polars collect
